  m_text: "After you doused your liquid into the \nsystem, you must deal with the
    \nconsiquences of those effects.\nYou must be able to do your day to day tasks\nwhile
    taking being affected by whatever you \ndrank.\n\nAfter introducing the substance
    into your \nsystem, you must face the consequences of its \neffects. These challenges
    can range from \ndriving to attending a job interview. Your \nobjective is to
    continue navigating your life \nwithout letting these effects cause you to fail
    \nyour tasks."
